::Create hashmap implementation
:: Xnet_base and xnet_utils should not need to include any addon headers.
:: However any addon should be able to include xnet_base and xnet_utils.

== Within 'xnet_addon_chat.h' ==
xnet_integrate_chat_addon(); // Appends all of chat's functionalities
    - [Hashmap] {unique_addon_feature_number} : {feature's 'perform' function}
    - All of the addon's functions must use this signature "int <chat_perform_'xyz'>(xnet_box_t *, xnet_active_connection_t *);"

